_sText:
Hi, bananas,
I made another map based on real location.
Advertising agency where I am employed bought abandoned building and reconstructed to modern office complex. Original proportions of building don't provide much tactical options (original reconstruction map included), so I upgraded mainly interiors. Check my WIP 

Features:
  • 3D skybox
  • soundscapes (office, assault)
  • randomly spawned hostages
  • broken walls and barriers in halls
  • access to exterior allowed
  • custom models of Skoda cars
  • few custom textures

This is beta version (released it for test purposes) Please see and download final version. 

If you like this one, check all of my maps here
This map or its parts is also used in my singleplayer mod

Have a fun
Dinus Saurus
